 <br />\n<br />\n係爆時高熱下, D水銀係咪會氣化, 方圓數百米都冚家鏟？</blockquote><br />\n水銀加熱=kabomb"},{"pid":"8f8be1966235d4d2a1792b9fb6e408ecf9f894d1","tid":199902,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T14:49:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>爆到一地水銀玩野吖細佬</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n但我之前睇《巴札爾的軍靴》, 佢教個水銀起爆係好細舊<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/2/28/Mercuryswitch.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2F2%2F28%2FMercuryswitch.jpg&h=5d79fe05&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n照計點爆都唔會好大鑊...<br />\n<br />\n唔明華仔句對白點解...<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b88c6e9f3007b9b8c74255c80cbfd14d34c85c9","tid":199902,"uid":39750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-13T14:56:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>關於劉德華電影《拆彈專家》既劇情, 唔係好明<br />\n<br />\n壓力煲炸彈係乜原理? <br />\n點解簡單一個壓力煲都可以製成炸彈既?<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.yes-news.com/201606/lTn6ZhSz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.yes-news.com%2F201606%2FlTn6ZhSz.jpg&h=90ea8247&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外, 點解水銀引信唔可以即場引爆?<br />\n我係好識, 睇戲睇到一頭霧水...<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n爆到一地水銀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />玩野吖細佬</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我想問, 如果<strong>水銀</strong>既話, <br />\n<br />\n係爆時高熱下, D水銀係咪會氣化, 方圓數百米都冚家鏟？</blockquote><br />\n水銀加熱=kabomb</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.answers.yahoo.com/question/index?qid=20101003000015KK07894\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.answers.yahoo.com%2Fquestion%2Findex%3Fqid%3D20101003000015KK07894&d=5G%2Bx0n%2BFJXS0hP%2BJIuhjgkbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=8d934042\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.answers.yahoo.com/question/index?qid=20101003000015KK07894</a><br />\n自己睇 簡單啲講水銀太高溫或者太多movement , 水銀流動<br />\n在玻璃管中會有兩